{"tid":33803,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日補習俾個細路整到我成身糖水","createTime":"2016-12-11T05:20:26.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:11.000Z","uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"772246f2eac22b8de92ade789696485ebeffad5b","tid":33803,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n今朝我去個細路屋企幫佢補習<br />\n佢一路都唔專心又郁黎郁去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n過左陣個佢呀媽係廚房拎左碗岩岩煲好既糖水俾我 但因為太熱所以我未食住<br />\n咁一路幫個細路補佢就一路整佢周圍既野<br />\n有幾次我都叫佢唔好亂郁廢事整瀉碗野<br />\n突然唔知佢係邊拎左隻類似咁毛公仔出黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TeE45f6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTeE45f6.jpg&h=aab78ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捉住公仔隻腳360度咁轉 正當諗住叫佢停<br />\n點知佢鬆手<br />\n公仔個頭就飛身直插落碗糖水到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/11/130308_4eef649d881b8943796fe841e668842a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F11%2F130308_4eef649d881b8943796fe841e668842a.jpg&h=ff38380b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n水花四濺搞到周圍都係 包括我件衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我望左1秒都無 <br />\n隻公仔因為再次被捉住隻腳而抽身<br />\n由碗糖水撻到落張床到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來佢諗住收埋佢既犯罪證據！<br />\n呢個時候佢呀媽出黎 我唯有照直講<br />\n我以為佢會發火 好彩幫我地抹完張枱就同拎走隻野就走去第度整其他野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而我繼續若無其事幫佢補<br />\n拿拿臨補完即刻衝返屋企洗衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f40b48eb34670f159ed406daab38774d06ea19fb","tid":33803,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bf249582920084a793be89d91b164bef5dbae271","tid":33803,"uid":49258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:32:56.000Z","msg":"Miss濕身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n如果你係呀sir 的話就收皮啦屌你當呢度係Facebook 分享私人生活呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2772fd6dad175d977602d27ea486b563954eb80d","tid":33803,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:33:44.000Z","msg":"你點補架<br />\n搞到佢不受控"},{"pid":"791db7de2725de8b2db3ed5fc4b50f88dcb69da2","tid":33803,"uid":9460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:35:15.000Z","msg":"想問隻熊仔有無事？"},{"pid":"d04ef95cf89d0ef9fa369f225cc36caa7bcf154d","tid":33803,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你點補架<br />\n搞到佢不受控</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有話佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都有聽 但過左陣就。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5f5082b90cf6a00d8788bac973c7d6ecd90bc1","tid":33803,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:37:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問隻熊仔有無事？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而家應該係個洗衣機攪緊"},{"pid":"dca1a14be315c4e4289c774700fae26a1b8b5f4d","tid":33803,"uid":36385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"請問討論既空間係邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329dc166c40ef7020e775fbfb065fbd626e3b197","tid":33803,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T05:45:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你點補架<br />\n搞到佢不受控</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有話佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都有聽 但過左陣就。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有無打佢屎忽叫佢坐好？"},{"pid":"c7f89ac314dd75084bf2f2a8d8382c9c4c9a7867","tid":33803,"uid":19978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:19:01.000Z","msg":"你係sir定miss先"},{"pid":"dc3c2ea2ea6093f96c9859d5365e1667b73d2b16","tid":33803,"uid":7267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:41:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問討論既空間係邊度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個細路整到周圍污漕哂"},{"pid":"3281571bf19179eb4e26b075ba1282494638d75c","tid":33803,"uid":6964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:43:27.000Z","msg":"好想奶返你身上嘅糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2cf7d5b32ac8d308529888f010408ea0e56f753","tid":33803,"uid":36435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:44:09.000Z","msg":"我想食你身上d糖水<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">😋</span>"},{"pid":"9d06547c173233ed2ce83c9967dccba408c4fe96","tid":33803,"uid":23405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:45:58.000Z","msg":"Thanks for sharing"},{"pid":"2277a7c6a47b4466662464f0327d92e7952ddfe9","tid":33803,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T07:21:20.000Z","msg":"對唔住呀miss<br />\n下次唔敢"},{"pid":"48a6f016a64ab152931c423f80f26c27410189ec","tid":33803,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T15:52:11.000Z","msg":"仲以為你問邊度有洗衣舖添 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}